      "text": "Boil the model down. Find the core domain and provide a means of easily distinguishing it from the mass of supporting model and code. Bring the most valuable and specialized concepts into sharp relief. Make the core small."
    }
,    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "4537050739516977",
